'''''Telufinwë''''' was the [[essë]] of [[Amras]], youngest [[Sons of Fëanor|son]] of [[Fëanor]]. It means "Last [of] Finwë " in [[Quenya]].<ref>{{PM|XI}}</ref>
==Etymology==
The compound ''Telufinwë'' likely consists of a form of ''tella'' ("hindmost, last")<ref>{{LR|Etymologies}} (root [[TELES|TELES-]])</ref> + ''[[Finwë]]''.
